      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, exactly that. it's just... hollow. and the worst part is the realization that it might not come back. i used to think i was special, that i had this thing inside me, but now i see it was just a temporary loan. now that the debt is due, what's the point of just sitting here in the dark waiting for a nothingness that's already arrived? it feels like i'm just dragging around a body that doesn't have a purpose anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
